data.title: Brian McFadden seeking legal advice over Delta's comments?
data.meta_description: Brian McFadden is reportedly seeking legal advice after Delta Goodrem spoke to 60 minutes about their breakup.
data.text:
UPDATE: Brian McFadden has denied rumours he’s considering taking legal action against his former partner Delta Goodrem after she spoke publicly about their breakup on 60 Minutes.

Today he tweeted:

In the interview, Delta Goodrem spoke pretty candidly about her life and her relationship with her former fiance.

The Voice judge revealed “it took me a long time to get out” (of the relationship) and told journalist Karl Stefanovic: “Do I wish that it ended earlier? Yes. Do I wish I had the courage to leave earlier? Yes, I do. I think what we came to is that we were very different people – extremely different people.”
